Class Server_UI

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • application.Server_UI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUI_Interface_Server, java.lang.Runnable

    public class Server_UI
extends java.lang.Thread
implements GUI_Interface_Server
    This is the UI used for the chat-server. It extends GUI_Interface_Server class, witch makes it compatible with the server class. The overridden methods in this class is used by the server to control the UI.
    Author:
    Fredrik Johansson, Mattias Edin
